This document is a binding legal and ethical contract that governs the use of the Software (as defined below). The Software was engineered in Kyiv, Ukraine, during an active information war, as an instrument for intellectual defense. Its designated function is to deconstruct manipulative narratives to serve the cause of clarity and critical thinking.

This license is structured with maximal clarity to protect this core mission. It grants specific freedoms under the condition of absolute adherence to its principles. By accessing, using, copying, modifying, or distributing any part of the Software, you irrevocably agree to all terms and conditions herein. Violation of any clause will result in the immediate and automatic termination of all rights granted to you under this agreement.

