B.2. GENERATED ANALYSIS IS NOT A STATEMENT OF FACT: The Generated Analysis is the probabilistic output of a third-party large language model and is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a "truth verdict" or professional advice. Reliance on the Generated Analysis for any decision-making is strictly at your own risk.
