Your right to use, modify, or distribute the Software is conditional upon your strict adherence to the following restrictions. Violation of any of these restrictions results in immediate termination of this license.

C.1. PROHIBITED USES: The Software shall not be used, directly or indirectly, for any of the following purposes:
a) State-Sponsored Disinformation: Use by any state-level actor, intelligence agency, or state-affiliated entity for the purpose of creating, refining, or disseminating propaganda or disinformation.
b) Suppression of Speech: Integration into any system designed for the automated censorship, moderation, or suppression of lawful speech.
c) Surveillance: Use in any application related to mass surveillance, social scoring, or predictive policing.
d) Military Application: Use in any military, intelligence, or offensive cyberwarfare operations.
e) Harassment: Use to generate content intended to harass, defame, intimidate, or harm any individual or group.

